init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Of course, your Majesty," said the bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Because you are the Queen, of course," said the bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Since the day you were born, your Majesty," said the bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I shall do whatever you command," said the bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You would, but I would die with you," said the bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I even tried to tell the others about the bee, but they all thought I was crazy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: After all, why would I believe a tiny bee could talk?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: A few days later, I was stung by a bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was just a normal bee.
